cdata.name: Opair
cdata.desc:
Opair is a cryptocurrency platform that supports Colored Coins and Smart Contracts (with a functional programming languages).Opair is fueld by XPO tokens, a Proof of Stake cryptocurrency with a 60 avg. second blocktime.

Opair features a Market place with a decentralized reputation system, a Crowfunding platform, anAlias System, andDecentralized debit cards.Users can also start aconfigurableprivate blockchains using Opair.
